## SORUMLU KATMANLAR
Tam bileşen listesi: `docs/33-LAYER-MANIFEST.yaml` (KATMAN 7–15, 20, 23–24, 27–29)

- **KATMAN 7–8** — İş Mantığı + Veri: Domain, Use Cases, Repository, Sync Layer
- **KATMAN 9** — Offline-First (V1 zorunlu): Local First, Sync Queue, Offline Search/Actions
- **KATMAN 10–11** — Cache + Ağ: Multi-Level Cache, HTTP/3, Circuit Breaker
- **KATMAN 12–13** — Medya + Arama: Playback Pipeline, Semantic/Hybrid Search
- **KATMAN 14–15** — AI + Kişiselleştirme: On-device ML, Preference/Intent Engine
- **KATMAN 20** — Güvenilirlik: Fault Tolerance, Self Healing, Graceful Degradation
- **KATMAN 23–24** — Dağıtık Sistemler + Veri Altyapısı (V2): Microservices, PostgreSQL, Redis
- **KATMAN 27** — Otomasyon: CI/CD, Automated Testing, Deployment, Rollback
- **KATMAN 28** — Platform: SDK Layer, Public API, Plugin/Extension System
- **KATMAN 29** — Ekosistem: Third Party, Partner Network, White Label

